{TRIPLE BREAKER}
■ When you summon this creature or whenever this creature attacks, choose up to 2 creatures and return them to their owner's hand.
■ Whenever your opponent puts a creature or casts a spell, you may skip the rest of the turn.

{TRIPLE BREAKER}
■ At the end of each turn, each player discards their hand.
